EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO CRIMINAL OFFENSES -- PUBLIC UTILITIES
***
1 This act would expand the meaning of bomb threats and false reports to include any
2 warning or threat of the existence of an explosive device and/or which that prompts a law
3 enforcement response and allows a judge to impose conditions of bail to include extreme risk
4 protection orders, no trespass orders and counseling.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
